column5: So are any of you Ontario boys going to be doing the B1? I hope to see some of you there.
I want to be going to be a scrutineer again hopefully. I'm gonna board your ship! Or be more involved in some other way...
I will be fishing it again this year, would not miss it for the world.
Marvin, u fishing with blake again this year?
Hey bud, Yes I am. Give me a call tomorrow to arrange a day for lakers. 647-709-6278. I will be going up again soon.
